{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/TopImage3.png?t=1716563952\" /><br><br>IGNISTONE is a roguelike action game that focuses on parry.<br>The game is easy to play, yet includes intense combat,<br>strategic roguelike game-play, and even many minigames!<br><strong>*Mouse controls only. Controllers are not supported.</strong><br><br>Set to an amazing adventure to uncover the mystery of IGNISTONE!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/Border1.png?t=1716563952\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/EngChnTown4.gif?t=1716563952\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The town</h2>The start of the adventure is this village where the Mame tribe lives.<br><br>Interact with the diverse Mame tribe members and create body armor that suits your playstyle!<br><br>Fun fact : Mame (pronounced MA-MAY) means bean in Japanese.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/Divide3.png?t=1716563952\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/EngChnBattle.gif?t=1716563952\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The battle</h2>IGNISTONE focuses on a 1 vs 1 combat.<br><br>Your options are limited to &quot;Attack,&quot; &quot;Defense,&quot; and &quot;Special Move&quot;.<br>This enhances the tension of the roguelike gameplay.<br>Focus on the enemy's movement and time your parry!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/Divide3.png?t=1716563952\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/EngDungeon.gif?t=1716563952\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Dungeon</h2>Once you create your battle armor, it's time to enter the dungeon!<br><br>Many treasures and enemies are awaiting you!<br>Strategically choose the best route out of three and keep moving forward!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/Divide3.png?t=1716563952\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/EngOmamori.gif?t=1716563952\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Weapons and Amulets</h2>There are many amulets and weapons in this game.<br><br>You can equip one sword and one shield, and up to eight amulets.<br>Find your unique combination from a diverse range of equipments!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/Divide3.png?t=1716563952\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/EngQuiz.gif?t=1716563952\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Minigames</h2>IGNISTONE is not all about the dungeon.<br><br>It has many small minigames!<br>Enjoy the playful world of IGNISTONE!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393890/extras/TagSleep.png?t=1716563952\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Adventure","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2393890/02431d898d61a40bb303103c484e379661014a8a.jpg"},{"name":"Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2393890/e8377bae5f1708331626ea828a8addccfe6b7cbf.jpg"},{"name":"Parry Beginner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2393890/2a7fc25aae3de833527dec8df4bb46bb83fc0a76.jpg"},{"name":"Parry Expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2393890/240275db40cc71ec7134e34c8f243286e0e183d6.jpg"},{"name":"Quiz Master","path":"https://cdn.akama